**Summary:** This documentation covers Amplitude's Engagement Matrix chart feature, which analyzes feature engagement patterns using a four-quadrant matrix view based on breadth (% active users) and frequency (times/days performed) metrics, supporting up to 100 events with options for Top Events, Bottom Events, and custom event selection.

